                <mxCell id="note-mapping" value="Analyze endpoint returns immediately after queueing.&#xa;Frontend polls the status endpoint until completion.&#xa;Worker merges LanguageTool and spaCy detector results.&#xa;If ENABLE_ADVANCED_GERMAN_CHECKS is true,&#xa;also run AdvancedGermanGrammarDetector&#xa;(subordinate clauses, feminine agreement, würde + infinitive).&#xa;Post-process with SpacyTextProcessor:&#xa;• categorize_error() — POS-based override&#xa;• extract_error_context() — JSON metadata&#xa;• get_pos_tag() — spacy_pos_tag field&#xa;Deduplicate by offset range." style="shape=note;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontSize=10;fontStyle=2;fillColor=#f5f5f5;strokeColor=#666666;fontColor=#333333;size=14;" parent="1" vertex="1">
